CIMAC pixel clustering - normalize by total (frequencies, no calibration), iter thresh = 2

Candace Liu

November 2, 2020

  • Gaussian blur sigma=2, no arcsinh, k=20
  • z-score cap=3 for hierarchical clustering, iterative z-score threshold=2
  • For each pixel, divide each marker by total (each pixel sums to 1)
  • NO calibration channel for normalization
  • No iterations in iterative clustering

No z-score cap for hierarchical clusters

Z-score cap=3 for hierarchical clusters
